简介 INFOWelcome to U.I.E. City, a place of amazement and wonder.This has been in the planning phases for a long time And has taken a lot of time for construction. But now finally it has neared final completion, with all 5 districts almost complete.Give it a diamond on planet Minecraft if you like it!欢迎来到U.I.E城市，这是一个富有惊奇的城市。这个地图拥有很长一段时间的计划时间，还有很长的时间来建造。现在他已经块完全完成了，有5个区快完成请在PMC给钻石如果你喜欢的话
